headline: A. O. Smith: Benefiting From The Twin Tailwinds Of Water And Efficiency
summary: A. O. Smith moved its revenue from $2.5 billion in FY 2015 to $3.8 billion in FY 2024, a compound annual growth rate of 4.8%.
